data.description: Just steps away from the World's Most Famous Beach where sun, surf, and sand await at your doorstep is where you will find this low-maintenance home. Nestled in a prime location just a few blocks from the iconic coastline, this charming beach home offers the perfect blend of relaxation and excitement for those seeking the ultimate coastal lifestyle. As you step inside, you're greeted by a bright and airy living space with abundant natural light. The open floor plan connects the living, and kitchen areas, creating an inviting atmosphere for gatherings with family and friends. The well-equipped kitchen features Samsung appliances, Granite counters, a deep under-mount sink, Shaker soft close cabinetry, and a breakfast bar, making it a chef's delight for preparing beachside meals or entertaining guests. Whether you're hosting a barbecue on the spacious patio or enjoying a quiet dinner indoors, this kitchen is sure to inspire culinary creativity. Additional highlights of this beachside oasis include Custom Lighting, 2013 Storm Windows, an updated Electrical panel, a Rheen water heater, a 2018 Roof, an Updated Custom shower, a 2017 Carrier HVAC with a Sensi Thermostat, a Jacuzzi, above ground garden, and a privacy fenced backyard oasis, perfect for outdoor entertaining or simply lounging in the sun. Whether you're seeking a full-time residence, a vacation getaway, or an investment property, this beach home offers endless possibilities for coastal living. The Solar panels stay with a 30-year transferrable loan that saves $ in monthly electric bills.  Don't miss your chance to make your dreams of beachside living a reality. Schedule your private tour today and discover the unparalleled charm and allure of life just blocks away from the world's most famous beach.
